#Privacy Policy

- OnMonday Privacy Policy -

By using and installing the OnMonday apps, you agree to this Privacy Policy and give explicit and informed consent to the processing of your data. If you do not agree, please do not install or use the OnMonday apps.

Data Collection and Use

We do not personally identify you. We may collect and use the following data for functional purposes:

- Device call state
- Microphone
- Camera
- Sensor data
- Other device properties

Some OnMonday apps may request your location data for functional purposes. Your GPS location data will not be accessed without your explicit consent.

Data Sharing

We do not share your GPS location or any personal user data with third parties.

Your Consent

By using and installing the OnMonday apps, you consent to the collection and use of your data as outlined in this Privacy Policy.

If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us.
